data.description: Discover the charm of 1381 Payne Ave, with classic features that include a welcoming front porch, crystal knobs, tall baseboards, and hardwood floors. This delightful home boasts 9' ceilings, creating a spacious and airy feel. The large upstairs bedroom exudes character, offering a cozy retreat. Step into the backyard oasis, enclosed by an 8' privacy fence, with a deck perfect for entertaining. Lake Phalen is a short walk away, providing a scenic escape, while downtown St. Paul is just minutes by car. Experience the perfect blend of timeless charm & comfort at 1381 Payne Ave. Schedule a tour today!
